-- hero.hero: `malai` - SSH Replacement with P2P Networking

malai provides remote access to your machines and services using peer-to-peer 
networking. Execute commands on remote machines, organize infrastructure 
into clusters, and manage distributed systems without central servers or 
certificate authorities.

