-- ds.heading-medium: Key Features

-- feature-item: üîê P2P Security

Each machine has unique cryptographic identity. Only cluster members can connect.
Direct verification without passwords or certificate authorities.

-- feature-item: üì° Remote Command Execution

Execute commands on any machine in your cluster via P2P networking.
`malai web01.company ps aux` runs directly on the target machine.

-- feature-item: üåê Multi-Cluster Support

Organize different environments into separate clusters.
Personal, staging, production - each with their own access control.

-- end: ds.column

-- end: ftd.desktop

